{"id":416884,"date":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":13}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"112","ytitle":"","mtitle":"球场内外","ftitle":"","authors":["袁鹰"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球场内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲的好手绝技竞呈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球场外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月的东风荡漾人心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风吹得游人醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球场内外处处喜盈盈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球场内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万千颗心儿跳不停；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球场外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万人凝神屏息候佳音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"襟上新佩着彩色梅花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为北京的大好春光又添一片锦!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月九日北京"}]}